Remember Me 100% 'Sketch U' in their latest teaser for comeback By jennywill 7 minutes ago 765 24 0 0 Google+ 100% has released an MV teaser for their comeback! The boys will be coming back with their next mini-album ' Sketchbook ' and title song " Sketch U ". Leader Minwoo is the male lead for the MV, and fans can also hear Rokhyun and Hyukjin 's high notes as a little preview into the song. 
Check out the teaser above and get ready for the 22nd! YOU MAY LIKE GET AKP IN YOUR INBOX! ..or follow allkpop to stay updated: Tags:
